==English==

===Etymology===
From Jamaican slang, a sound suggested by the quality of light reflected by diamonds, adopted by American rappers. Compare words of similar sound and meaning: {{m|en|blink}}, {{m|en|blinding}}, {{m|en|blank}}.

Possible connection with Indonesian beling, shards of glass.

